      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior appointments, reflects an uncompromising standard of maintenance. This is an investment-grade example intended for the most discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
