      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to be listing this absolute beauty. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there's not a single blemish to be found. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
