    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis maintains its original rigidity with no signs of subframe stress, while the suspension retains factory-correct damping characteristics. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment, with all maintenance intervals strictly observed to ensure the high-revving valvetrain and cooling system operate at peak efficiency. A true collector-grade specimen for those seeking a pure, analog driving experience.",
